            <p class="mb-5">
              We are committed to safeguarding your personal information and providing a secure experience while using our services to browse events, purchase tickets, or manage events. Please take a moment to read through our privacy practices below.
            </p>
            <div class="row gy-4 gy-md-0 gx-xxl-5">
              <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                <div class="d-flex">
                  <div class="me-4 text-primary">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-shield-lock" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                      <path d="M5.5 8a1.5 1.5 0 1 1 3 0v2h-3V8zm2.493-6.901a.5.5 0 0 1 .014 0H7.508a.5.5 0 0 1-.014 0L7.497.099a1.007 1.007 0 0 0-.82.382L3.6 4H1a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V5a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-2.6L9.32.481a1.007 1.007 0 0 0-.82-.382zM8 1.467c.31 0 .55.206.69.398l3.181 4.221a.5.5 0 0 1 .119.372v5.542a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H1a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V6.458a.5.5 0 0 1 .119-.372L3.3 1.865A1.008 1.008 0 0 1 4 1.467h4zM7.5 10v1a.5.5 0 1 0 1 0v-1a.5.5 0 0 0-1 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Data Protection</h2>
                    <p class="text-secondary mb-0">
                      Your personal data, including payment details and contact information, is encrypted and stored securely. We employ the latest security protocols to ensure your data is protected at all times.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                <div class="d-flex">
                  <div class="me-4 text-primary">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-person-fill-check" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                      <path d="M15.854 5.146a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-6.5 6.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-3-3a.5.5 0 1 1 .708-.708l2.646 2.647 6.146-6.147a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0z"/>
