                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3">User Consent</h2>
                    <p class="text-secondary mb-0">
                      We only collect and process your information with your consent, whether for creating an account, purchasing tickets, or managing events. You can review and update your preferences anytime through your account settings.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h4 class="mt-5">Information We Collect</h4>
            <p class="text-secondary">
              We collect information that helps us provide better services to you, such as your name, email address, payment details, and preferences. This data is essential for creating your account, processing ticket purchases, and offering personalized event recommendations.
            </p>
            <h4 class="mt-5">How We Use Your Data</h4>
            <p class="text-secondary">
              We use your information to facilitate ticket purchases, send event notifications, and improve our platform. We do not share your data with third parties without your explicit consent, except where required by law.
            </p>
            <h4 class="mt-5">Your Privacy Rights</h4>
            <p class="text-secondary">
              You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information at any time. For any privacy-related requests or concerns, feel free to contact our support team.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
